com/user/41351/</a><br />\n<br />\n第一頁可以睇到會員既summary（click &quot;View All Posts&quot;到第二頁）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GebxOHi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGebxOHi.png&h=5a5c8f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二頁可以睇到會員既所有post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97c1G2E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97c1G2E.png&h=fc5dfe65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係用免費server，所以會慢。<br />\n歡迎意見及批評。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"好波<br />\n我記得PTT 有類似系統<br />\n可以睇個人幾點出post<br />\n如果永遠9-5出POST, 就大機會係水軍<br />\n<br />\n可以加個功能落去"},{"pid":"a1faf3ef4da5ae96317ec4de38a53f70cf238416","tid":1370632,"uid":51143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"唔記得講，第一頁最上方如果見到係&quot;Running&quot;而唔係&quot;Completed&quot;，表示server揾緊會員既posts，請等約1分鐘後再refresh一次就有野睇。"},{"pid":"48f46489eca67a21905a6a7002f04976ee4759c1","tid":1370632,"uid":196871,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"其實呢樣係雙面刃<br />\n比五毛或者警察拎嚟用就唔係幾好<br />\n建議樓主收返埋"},{"pid":"118dfbd397a50cc669c1d7b3ad16cde673e7b8d3","tid":1370632,"uid":258409,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"48f46489eca67a21905a6a7002f04976ee4759c1","tid":1370632,"uid":196871,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"其實呢樣係雙面刃<br />\n比五毛或者警察拎嚟用就唔係幾好<br />\n建議樓主收返埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"其實本身呢個SERVER顯示嘅內容暫時睇落同連登本身起到嘅無咩分別，只係UI好過連登本身起底系統，應該無問題"},{"pid":"503d10dabe9247236175245c3454f36644a984ee","tid":1370632,"uid":37713,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"48f46489eca67a21905a6a7002f04976ee4759c1","tid":1370632,"uid":196871,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"其實呢樣係雙面刃<br />\n比五毛或者警察拎嚟用就唔係幾好<br />\n建議樓主收返埋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"其實政府裡面已經有晒成個system mark低晒我地講啲野架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我搵唔返幅圖<br />\n佢係成個db咁既<br />\n每個record有齊晒樓主 post名 回覆內容 回覆人既名 咩台"},{"pid":"ac63c52159d69e07bb1eaa724b23d65a848af77f","tid":1370632,"uid":51143,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T23:57:58.000Z","msg":"有人擔心會唔會俾五毛或警察用，其實不用太擔心。因為一個咁簡單既工具，人地咁多資源，一定做得到同類既工具，而且做得更好；相反普通市民如果有咁工具，有一個更方便既途徑去起底，可以幫助平衡返政府或其他組織利用連登作宣傳工具。<br />\n<br />\n有提議經常半夜出post既可能係五毛，多謝提醒，會諗下有咩可以做。"},{"pid":"d9184b932b98eb376d7b82cac3c9daf1860e1632","tid":1370632,"uid":23953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T00:39:10.000Z","msg":"連仔有時會刪自爆post<br />\n你打算點做？日日重新scan一次有冇刪post?"},{"pid":"d847d5ae09c5a1251693c69a7d89384780123c89","tid":1370632,"uid":8294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03768e4e815a5d95901863b4b7b1cba644255469","tid":1370632,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:34:01.000Z","msg":"Good<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更易分辦五毛定膠"},{"pid":"877765962082a62f463e32771a5f39ac42248a13","tid":1370632,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:54:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Ziqytpr.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiqytpr.jpg&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=b077b225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/Ziqytpr.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Ltrawfg.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtrawfg.jpg&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=a8fc47b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/Ltrawfg.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/JzCtk0t.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihk